Output hero.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.6

Type "veles" Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "In one sentence, what is this project about?"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 14s
Ctrl+D
Sleep 1s
